      <title>尼日利亚将能源价格提高近三倍，保留对穷人的补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/nigeria-to-almost-triple-energy-prices-keep-subsidy-for-poor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士表示，尼日利亚计划在几周内将能源价格提高近两倍，以吸引新投资并削减约 23 亿美元的关税上限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/nigeria-to-almost-triple-energy-prices-keep-subsidy-for-poor</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:40:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
