    <item>
      <title>特洛伊·盖耶斯基表示，固定收益风险回报仍然并不理想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-02/fixed-income-risk-reward-still-isn-t-fantastic-gayeski-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[FS Investments 首席市场策略师 Troy Gayeski 表示，“曲线后端存在利率大幅上升的重大风险”，并且可能会重新测试 5% 的水平。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-02/fixed-income-risk-reward-still-isn-t-fantastic-gayeski-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:21:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财务困境加剧，碧桂园销售额进一步下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/country-garden-extends-sales-slump-as-financial-woes-pile-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[碧桂园控股有限公司(Country Garden Holdings Co.)上个月的房屋销售量较上年同期大幅下滑，这给这家已经面临清盘申请并错过了发布年度业绩的最后期限的中国开发商带来了更大的麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/country-garden-extends-sales-slump-as-financial-woes-pile-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:19:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界银行将批准向肯尼亚提供 12 亿美元预算资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/world-bank-set-to-approve-1-2-billion-budget-funding-for-kenya</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行准备在 4 月底之前批准向肯尼亚提供 12 亿美元的预算融资，为这个希望减少对商业债务依赖的东非国家提供关键融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/world-bank-set-to-approve-1-2-billion-budget-funding-for-kenya</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:17:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SLB 将以 78 亿美元收购油田服务竞争对手 ChampionX</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/slb-to-buy-oilfield-service-company-championx-in-all-stock-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SLB 同意以 78 亿美元的全股票交易收购竞争对手油田服务提供商 ChampionX Corp.，此举将扩大 SLB 的投资组合，因为老化的页岩油田意味着美国钻探商需要更好的技术来维持石油和天然气生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/slb-to-buy-oilfield-service-company-championx-in-all-stock-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 11:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场降息幅度再次低于美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/markets-back-to-seeing-fewer-rate-cuts-than-the-federal-reserve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周有一段时间，市场和美联储对于货币宽松的步伐达成了共识。这种情况并没有持续多久，国债投资者正在付出代价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/markets-back-to-seeing-fewer-rate-cuts-than-the-federal-reserve</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 10:20:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧佩克减产和地缘政治风险推动油价上涨至 85 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国原油期货自 10 月份以来首次突破 85 美元，这是在 OPEC+ 减产、需求强劲和地缘政治风险加剧的背景下市场反弹的最新里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美联储推迟降息，债券抛售加剧：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员消化了美联储今年降息幅度较小的可能性，美国国债扩大抛售，股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
